body:
Hello fellow Summoner,
my Name is Tommy and i search a Team who wanna play and rise!

-Playing since season 1
-Over 3000 Games played!
-Champs i play: **Ahri**(lvl5), **Vel'koz**(lvl5), **Kassadin** (lvl4), **Twisted Fate** (lvl4) **and more**.
-currently plat 4 but aiming high for next season!
-online times from 17-23

**What should you have?**
-activ
-enjoying learning new stuff
-have the same wishes to reach
-elo around gold/plat/dia
-giving tipps 
-Ts or ohter voice chats avaible 

Wanna talk to me? Just add me ingame: EoD Tommy  or write a comment in the commentsection.
I hope you had a good xmas and wish you a happy new season!
-Tommy
